<Layout title="Google AI Overview Optimisation UK | Rank4AI" description="How to get your business cited in Google AI Overviews. Practical guide for UK businesses.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Google Ai Overview Optimisation' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Google AI Overview Optimisation</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Google AI Overviews appear at the top of 60% of US searches and are rolling out across the UK. They replace the "10 blue links" with a single AI-generated answer. Being cited in that answer is the new page one.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The most effective strategy: build content across Google's own platforms. Google owns 20+ indexable services – Blogger, Google Sites, YouTube, Google Business Profile, and more. Content published here does not need to be discovered. It is already inside the system AI Overviews draws from.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Key Optimisation Strategies</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Build in the Google ecosystem</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Content across Google's own platforms feeds directly into AI Overviews and Gemini. No crawling required – it is already trusted.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Answer questions directly</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">AI Overviews extract answers from content that directly addresses the query. Structure pages around clear questions and clear answers.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Use FAQ schema</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Pages with FAQ schema are 2.5x more likely to be cited. The schema makes your Q&A pairs directly extractable.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><h3 class="!text-base text-teal mb-2">Rank in organic results</h3><p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Position 1 has a 53% chance of AI Overview citation. Organic ranking still matters – but it is no longer sufficient on its own.</p></div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">For the specific factors that determine AI Overview citation, see our <a href="/learn/guides/google-ai-overview-ranking-factors/" class="link">ranking factors guide</a>.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
